The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Umpires may get fee hike

Mumbai: The BCCI umpires sub-committee has proposed to increase the fees of umpires by a substantial Rs 3000 per match day for all first class matches. 

BCCI vice-president and the chairman of the umpires sub-committee Lalit Modi said that this would take their fees to Rs 5000 per match day, from the present Rs 2000. (PTI) 




